ğŸŸ¢ Step 3: Create Your First FastAPI App
Create a file named main.py

from fastapi import FastAPI

app = FastAPI()

@app.get("/")def read_root():    
return {"message": "Hello FastAPI"}

ğŸŸ¢ Step 4: Run the Server
uvicorn main:app --reload

Open in browser:
